### 2. STORE BANNER SECTION
**Full-width banner area:**
- **Height**: 200-300px (desktop), 150-200px (tablet)
- **Content**:
  - Store banner image (cover)
  - OR promotional slider/carousel
  - Gradient overlay if needed for readability

### 3. STORE INFO BAR
**Below banner, full-width:**

**Left Side (60%):**
- **Store Identity**:
  - Store logo (80-96px circular) - positioned overlapping banner edge
  - Store name (24-28px, bold)
  - Verification badge
  - "Choice Store" / "Trends Store" badge if applicable
  
- **Stats Row** (below name):
  - Star rating (large) + rating count
  - Product count (e.g., "1.5K Items")
  - Follower count (e.g., "275K Followers")
  - Years active (e.g., "Since 2020")
  - Separator pipes between stats

- **Performance Badges** (horizontal row):
  - "500K+ Sold Recently" with fire icon
  - "99K+ Repeat Customers" with repeat icon
  - "Top Rated Seller" badge
  - Other achievements

**Right Side (40%):**
- **Action Buttons**:
  - "Follow Store" button (large, prominent)
    - Shows follower count
    - Changes to "Following" when active
  - "Chat Now" button (secondary style)
  - "Share Store" icon button

### 4. STORE NAVIGATION BAR (STICKY)
**Full-width navigation:**
- **Tabs/Links**:
  - "Home" (store homepage)
  - "All Products"
  - "Categories" (dropdown if many)
  - "New Arrivals"
  - "Best Sellers"
  - "Sale"
  - "Reviews"
  - "About"
- **Sticks** when scrolling past banner
- **Active state**: Underline or background highlight
- **Hover**: Color change

