## üé® DESKTOP VISUAL DESIGN

### DESIGN CONSISTENCY WITH LAKU  
**Critical**: Maintain visual consistency with your existing platform

**Your Current Laku Design:**
- **Layout**: Left sidebar navigation + main content area
- **Sidebar**: Fixed width, light background, simple icons with labels
- **Product Grid**: Multi-column (3-4 visible in screenshot)
- **Price Color**: Red (Rp) - bold and prominent
- **Original Price**: Gray, struck through
- **Sold Count**: "X+ terjual" in gray
- **Product Cards**: White, rounded corners, shadow or border
- **Product Images**: Rounded corners, clean aspect ratio
- **Search Bar**: Rounded, light background
- **Typography**: Clean sans-serif, clear hierarchy
- **Spacing**: Generous whitespace, clean and minimal

**Store Page Must Match:**
- Same sidebar styling (don't interfere with LAKU nav)
- Same product card design
- Same color scheme (red prices, gray secondary text)
- Same typography scale
- Same border radius values
- Same shadows and borders
- Consistent spacing patterns
- Button styles match existing design
- Same icon style

### Typography
- Store name: 24-28px, bold
- Section headers: 18-20px, semi-bold
- Product name: 14-16px
- Price: 18-22px, bold
- Body text: 14-16px
- Small text: 13-14px

### Spacing
- Container padding: 24-40px
- Section spacing: 32-48px
- Card padding: 16-20px
- Product gap: 16-20px

### Hover States
- Product cards: Elevation increase, image zoom
- Buttons: Color darken, slight scale
- Links: Color change, underline
- Filter options: Background highlight
- Images: Zoom or secondary image reveal

### Borders & Shadows
- Sidebar: Border right or subtle shadow
- Cards: Border or shadow-sm
- Elevated cards: shadow-md
- Active filters: Accent border

### Grid & Layout
- Max-width container: 1400-1600px
- Sidebar: 250-320px width
- Main area: Remaining space
- Gutters: 20-32px

---

## üîß DESKTOP FUNCTIONALITY

### Store Actions
- **Follow button**: 
  - Toggle follow/unfollow
  - Update follower count
  - Show tooltip on hover
  - Require login if not authenticated
- **Chat**: Open chat window or navigate to messages
- **Share**: Share menu with options (copy link, social media)

### Category & Filter
- **Category click**: Filter products, update URL
- **Filter change**: Update product grid
- **Auto-apply** OR "Apply" button
- **Clear filters**: Reset to default
- **Active filters**: Show as removable chips
- **URL updates**: Reflect filters for sharing/bookmarking

### Product Grid
- **Hover product**: Show secondary image, actions
- **Click product**: Navigate to product page
- **Quick view** (optional): Modal with product details
- **Add to wishlist**: Heart icon toggle
- **Quick add to cart**: Show size/variant selector if needed

### Sorting
- **Sort dropdown**: Change product order
- **Persist sort**: Remember across navigation
- **Combine with filters**: Apply both

### Pagination
- **Page click**: Load that page, scroll to top
- **Previous/Next**: Navigate pages
- **URL update**: Page number in URL
- **Keyboard**: Arrow keys navigation (optional)

### Search
- **Search input**: Auto-suggest as typing
- **Enter**: Execute search
- **Suggestions click**: Execute that search
- **Recent searches**: Click to re-search

### Reviews
- **Filter reviews**: Update display
- **Helpful button**: Increment count, disable after click
- **Review images**: Click to open lightbox
- **Sort reviews**: Reorder display
- **Load more**: Pagination or infinite scroll

---

## üìä DESKTOP DATA STRUCTURE

Same as mobile, with additions:

```typescript
{
  // ... all mobile fields
  collections: {
    id: string
    name: string
    description: string
    products: Product[]
  }[]
  topRatedProducts: Product[]
  newArrivals: Product[]
  bestSellers: Product[]
}
```

