## üéØ RESPONSIVE BREAKPOINTS

### Tablet (768px - 1023px)
- Sidebar: 30% width
- Product grid: 3 columns
- Smaller fonts and spacing
- Collapsible sidebar (optional)

### Small Desktop (1024px - 1279px)
- Sidebar: 25% width
- Product grid: 3-4 columns
- Standard spacing

### Medium Desktop (1280px - 1599px)
- Sidebar: 22% width
- Product grid: 4-5 columns
- Comfortable spacing

### Large Desktop (1600px+)
- Max-width container (1600px)
- Sidebar: 20% width
- Product grid: 5-6 columns
- Generous spacing

