## ‚ö° DESKTOP PERFORMANCE

- Lazy load images below fold
- Optimize images (600-1000px for products)
- Virtual scrolling for 500+ products
- Prefetch on hover (products)
- Cache filter state
- Debounce filter updates
- Fast pagination (< 500ms)
- Initial load < 2s

---

## üîê DESKTOP ACCESSIBILITY

- Keyboard navigation
- Focus indicators
- ARIA labels
- Screen reader friendly
- Skip to content
- Alt text for images
- Color contrast WCAG AA
- Semantic HTML

