- ‚úÖ All transitions are smooth
- ‚úÖ Page loads fast (< 2s)
- ‚úÖ Keyboard navigation works
- ‚úÖ Responsive across breakpoints
- ‚úÖ Accessibility standards met
- ‚úÖ URLs update with filters

